Usage: refineMacro [-help] [[[-area {x1 y1 x2 y2} [-selected ]]| -permutePack | -markStep | -restoreStep <integer> | -restoreMark <integer>] [-adjustPack ] [-ioPinClearance ] ]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-adjustPack             # adjust pack (bool, optional)
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # llx lly urx ury (box, optional)
-ioPinClearance         # io pin clear (bool, optional)
-markStep               # mark step (bool, optional)
-permutePack            # permute pack (bool, optional)
-restoreMark <integer>  # restore mark (int, optional)
-restoreStep <integer>  # restore step (int, optional)
-selected               # selected objects (bool, optional)